[normal]in 
[normal]England
[normal] 
[normal]can support improved work incentives. 
[normal]It has 
[normal]set out the key features of Universal Credit and how local authorities can apply a 
[normal]sensible means test to U
[normal]niversal 
[normal]C
[normal]redit
[normal] claimants in guidance and in the def
[normal]ault scheme. 
[normal]The Department 
[normal]and DCLG are 
[normal]also working to deliver data sharing so that claimants do not have to provide the same information to local authorities 
[normal]that 
[normal]they have already provided to 
[normal]the Department 
[normal]for their U
[normal]niversal 
[normal]C
[normal]redit
