[normal], which supports them to 
[normal]deliver
[normal] 
[normal]new homes
[normal]. It has 
[normal]develop
[normal]ed
[normal] Universal Credit in a way that protects 
[normal]landlords’
[normal] financial position.
[normal]9.3.
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
